auth api
    auth.createUser(username, secret, callback(token))
    auth.login(username, secret, callback(token))
    auth.refresh(username, oldToken, callback(newToken))
    https://firebase.google.com/docs/auth/admin/create-custom-tokens
    https://firebase.google.com/docs/auth/admin/manage-users#retrieve_user_data
    https://firebase.google.com/docs/reference/rest/auth/#section-refresh-token

To authenticate a user:
either pass in url &token=[...] or send in json {token:"..."}
verify id token
retrieve user data
make user variable available

